<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="28" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="28">• Small, tailless, hamsterlike, herbivorous lagomorphs with two pairs of incisors (one behind the other), large rounded ears, and soft fur.</paragraph>
